data.title: Category:Cheryl (singer)
data.text:
Cheryl Ann Tweedy (former last name Fernandez-Versini, previous last name Tweedy, born 30 June 1983 in Newcastle upon Tyne) is a British singer from England. She is widely known with the mononym as Cheryl and before that as Cheryl Cole because of her marriage with English footballer Ashley Cole. She is also a dancer and a television personality.
